## Design Decisions

1. **Separate ReelerBottomNavBar** — Created a dedicated nav bar instead of making the existing collector-app BottomNavBar generic, avoiding breaking changes to the collector app.
2. **RootNavigator toggle** — `isAuthenticated` defaults to `false` (auth flow). Set to `true` in code to review dashboard screens directly.
3. **Mock data centralized** — Every screen imports from a single `reelerMockData.ts` file. No screen has inline placeholder data.
4. **Every screen has TODO markers** — Each screen file has a header comment marking it for future WatermelonDB integration.

